artifacts.summary: Implementation plan v002 with detailed blocking analysis for all phases
Implementation summary documenting architectural limitations in FMP forward truth lemma

partial_progress.details: Forward truth lemma requires properties not available in IsLocallyConsistent (negation completeness, implication converse). Same architectural issue as TruthLemma.lean sorries.

blocking_reason: IsLocallyConsistent only captures soundness properties (modus ponens, T-axiom). Forward truth lemma requires completeness properties (negation completeness) only available for MCS-derived states. Box case also blocked by universal history quantification.
